      "title": "Counting of votes for the next President of India begins",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The counting of votes to elect the 15th President of India has begun.",
        "The contest is between the ruling National Democratic Alliance's Draupadi Murmu and opposition candidate Yashwant Sinha.",
        "The next president will be sworn in on July 25, and the presidency of India is only a nominal position."
      ],
